 <h2 id="challenges">10. Challenges Faced</h2>
<div class="challenges-section">
    <div class="challenge-item">
        <h3>Contextual Accuracy (RAG)</h3>
        <p><strong>Challenge:</strong> Ensuring the AI relied strictly on official college documents rather than generating external, unrelated information.</p>
        <p><strong>Solution:</strong> Implemented <em>LangChain</em> with a custom retrieval chain that forces the model to use source documents as the primary context before answering.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="challenge-item">
        <h3>Latency Management</h3>
        <p><strong>Challenge:</strong> Initial query response times were high due to large document processing.</p>
        <p><strong>Solution:</strong> Optimized the vector database search by implementing semantic caching and streaming responses to the frontend, reducing perceived wait time.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="challenge-item">
        <h3>Deployment Configuration</h3>
        <p><strong>Challenge:</strong> Setting up environment variables for the OpenAI/Gemini API on the production server (Vercel).</p>
        <p><strong>Solution:</strong> Configured secure environment variable management in Vercel settings to ensure API keys remained private while accessible to the backend.</p>
    </div>
</div>


